<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><img width="75" height="75" border="0" alt="After Inquiry, SAC Capital Says It Intends to Hire a Trading Monitor" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/02/26/business/dbpix-sac/dbpix-sac-square320.jpg"/><span class="title">After Inquiry, SAC Capital Says It Intends to Hire a Trading Monitor <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> Steven A. Cohen, the billionaire hedge fund owner, is looking to hire a former prosecutor or securities regulator to monitor trading at his investment firm after the federal governmentâs insider trading investigation.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/02/25/sac-capital-to-hire-a-trading-monitor/">DealBook &#187;</a></span></p>
