<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><!-- end .ru-story -->
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Elliott Raises Bid for Riverbed to $3.3 Billion <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> The hedge fund Elliott Management raised its bid for Riverbed Technology and continued to criticize the networking equipment company for failing to begin a process to sell itself.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/02/25/elliott-raises-bid-for-riverbed-to-3-3-billion/">DealBook &#187;</a></span></p>
</div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><!-- end .ru-story -->
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Paulsonâs Hedge Fund Seeks Puerto Rico Resort <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> The hedge fund Paulson &#038; Company, founded by the billionaire John A. Paulson, is in talks to buy a resort complex in Puerto Rico as it seeks to expand its investments on the beleaguered island, Bloomberg News writes.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-02-25/billionaire-paulson-said-in-talks-to-acquire-puerto-rico-resort.html"> BLOOMBERG NEWS </a></span></p>
