<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Lawsuit Against Zynga I.P.O. Dismissed <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> A federal court in San Francisco on Tuesday dismissed a lawsuit against Zynga in which shareholders claimed that Zynga misled them and inflated the value of its stock price ahead of and after its 2011 initial public offering, ReCode writes.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//recode.net/2014/02/25/zynga-beats-ipo-lawsuit/"> RECODE</a></span></p>
